1.Introduction

Start the Windows Machine and connect with the site view or with your own machine.I prefer my own machine and use the following 
command.

xfreerdp /u:username /p:password /v:machine_ip /dynamic-resolution

example:

xfreerdp /u:administrator /p:letmein123! /v:x.x.x.x /dynamic-resolution

